name: Club Compass
description: Club Compass is a webapp meant to improve the discovery and management of clubs and organizations at high-schools and universities. The club discovery process is fragmented and difficult to navigate. Club Compass aims to solve this problem by providing a centralized platform for students to discover, join, and manage clubs at their school. Club Compass is built with a modern tech stack and is designed to be scalable and maintainable.
